PP’s Saenz Says No Plans to Adjust Spanish Jobless Benefits

-- B y   A n g e l i n e   B e n o i t
-- 
2011-10-05T08:08:41Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-05/pp-s-saenz-says-no-plans-to-adjust-spanish-jobless-benefits.html
Spain ’s  People’s Party  has no plans
to adjust unemployment benefits and aims to encourage hiring if
it wins elections on Nov. 20, Soraya Saenz de Santamaria, the
party’s parliamentary spokeswoman, said today in  Madrid .  To contact the reporter on this story:
